    "recipeInstructions": [
        {
            "@type": "HowToStep",
            "text": "In a medium sized bowl, mix peanut butter, butter, sugar and rice krispies. Blend well until mixture forms a dough. Roll into 1-inch balls. Dip the balls into the melted chocolate until well coated. Place onto a cookie sheet lined with wax paper. Refrigerate for 30 minutes."
